  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="how-do-i-add-schema-markup-to-webflow">
      <span class="faq-q-text">How do I add schema markup to Webflow?</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="how-do-i-add-schema-markup-to-webflow"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Add JSON-LD schema through Page Settings &gt; Custom Code &gt; Head Code. Paste your schema script inside <code>&lt;script type="application/ld+json"&gt;</code> tags. For CMS templates, add schema to the collection template page settings. Webflow has no native schema builder, so manual injection is required.</p></div></div>
