  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="can-webflow-sites-rank-on-google">
      <span class="faq-q-text">Can Webflow sites rank on Google?</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="can-webflow-sites-rank-on-google"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, Webflow sites rank well on Google. Data from Ahrefs shows over 78% of Webflow sites rank in the top 20 for at least one keyword. The platform's clean code, fast hosting, and mobile responsiveness create strong ranking foundations. Success depends on content quality, keyword targeting, and backlink building, not just the platform.</p></div></div>
