    <div class="faq-a" id="does-webflow-automatically-generate-a-sitemap"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, Webflow auto-generates an XML sitemap at <code>yoursite.com/sitemap.xml</code>. You can enable or disable this in Site Settings &gt; SEO. Submit the sitemap to Google Search Console after launch. Update and resubmit whenever you make significant structural changes.</p></div></div>
